    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You have practiced techniques useful in melee combat against spellcasters, gaining the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When a creature within 5 feet of you casts a spell, you can use your reaction to make a melee weapon attack against that creature.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you damage a creature that is @status[concentration||concentrating] on a spell, that creature has disadvantage on the saving throw it makes to maintain its @status[concentration].</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on saving throws against spells cast by creatures within 5 feet of you.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
